}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>
    Before visitng us, there are a few things you should know:
    <br />
    We no longer require patients families, or visitors to wear masks at the hospital/ However, it may still be required in the following scenarios:
    <br />
    When patients are symptomatic, their visitors must wear a mask around the patient and in hallways.
    <br />
    Visitors may be required to wear a mask in outbreak units.
    <br />
    Before visiting, you must wash or sanitize your hands and follow the COVID-19 screen questions prior to entering.
</p>

<p style="text-align: center;" data-wahfont="18"><strong>If you are experiencing a medical emergency, please call 911</strong></p>